"content": "<h2>Literacy in the OT</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:14\">2KI 19:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:7\">2KI 5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:2\">2KI 23:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:2\">NEH 8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:29\">JER 29:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:61\">JER 51:61</a></p>\n<h2>Literacy in the NT</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:16\">LUK 4:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:28\">ACT 8:28</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:3\">REV 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:15\">ACT 13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:13\">2CO 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:4\">EPH 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:16\">COL 4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:27\">1TH 5:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:13\">1TI 4:13</a></p>\n<h2>The use of secretaries for reading and writing</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:8-2Kgs22:10\">2KI 22:8–22:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:18\">EZR 4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:23\">EZR 4:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth6:1\">EST 6:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer36:4\">JER 36:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:22\">ROM 16:22</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of literacy in Scripture</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:38\">NEH 9:38</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:8\">JHN 8:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:19\">PHM 1:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:24-Deut31:26\">DEU 31:24–31:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh18:9\">JOS 18:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:19\">1CH 28:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:63\">LUK 1:63</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:20\">JHN 19:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:27\">ACT 15:27</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of illiteracy in Scripture</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:12\">ISA 29:12</a></strong></p>",
